{"title":"沪杭线","authors":["周民"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":8,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"沪杭线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"周民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日落的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旅程浴着黄昏光；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的心盘桓如夕阳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要回故乡、难辨故乡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不敢说最后一班。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小站送来三月的风景，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"提筐拎包的月台在骚动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小女孩跨过道岔；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有江南美丽的地名不改。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想你的林荫、想你的弯道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忆垂柳和菜花无边；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轰然的铁桥下河水淌着乡音。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡村的烟囱挤出桑青，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水泥制件铺在田野，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝底白字的广告墙绵延。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有牛犁人锄的细作，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粪勺浇着宅边菜畦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赤脚走在田埂上的剪影。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争执是过去的日子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对视是别人的敏锐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去匆匆，回也空空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全程浴着黄昏光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的心境如夕阳的宁静。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}